# Web SQLi Checklist
## Per Website
```
[ ] Use nmap if possible to determine the database type
[ ] Check the website for any form submissions
  - Use burp to ensure data is being sent upon submission
```

## Per Input Field
```
[ ] Test for time-based injections
[ ] Try with a ' at the beginning
[ ] Try without a ' at the beginning
[ ] Try creating an error to see if a message is returned
[ ] Pivot to a shell via RCE if possible
[ ] Harvest database credentials
[ ] Pivot to a web shell with file write commands
```
